# Mintoscope demo. Install vhs (https://github.com/charmbracelet/vhs), then run:
#   vhs demo.tape
# Produces demo.gif. Add to the README with: ![demo](demo.gif)

Output demo.gif

Set FontSize 16
Set Width 1200
Set Height 760
Set Padding 18
Set Theme "Dracula"

Type "npm run audit -- 2b1kV6DkPAnxd5ixfnxCpjxmKwqjjaYmCZfHsFu24GXo"
Sleep 800ms
Enter
Sleep 7s
